WEBVTT

00:00:43.350 --> 00:00:50.990
[Sharp Blade in the Snow]

00:00:51.060 --> 00:00:53.930
[Episode 4] Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:01:17.600 --> 00:01:18.680
It's cold.

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:21.570
Standing barefoot on the floor

00:01:24.080 --> 00:01:26.240
will make you catch a chill.

00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:34.360
Your Majesty,

00:01:34.360 --> 00:01:36.200
Princess Royal heard that
your old illness has returned

00:01:36.200 --> 00:01:37.530
and sent some medicine.

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:41.800
I'll do it.

00:01:49.479 --> 00:01:51.009
This medicine is poisoned.

00:01:51.240 --> 00:01:52.440
I want to see

00:01:52.960 --> 00:01:55.360
if you'll really
drink this bowl of poison.

00:01:56.240 --> 00:02:00.170
The Princess Royal certainly chose well—
you really know how to serve.

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:16.520
You've caused serious trouble.

00:02:16.760 --> 00:02:17.640
Tell me,

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:19.610
how should I punish you?

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:21.960
Punishing me is nothing.

00:02:22.040 --> 00:02:24.640
But if you catch a chill,
that would be serious.

00:02:28.120 --> 00:02:28.920
Why not

00:02:29.960 --> 00:02:33.040
let me help you change your clothes?

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:43.720
Now you're really in trouble.

00:02:50.079 --> 00:02:52.760
Your Majesty, are you painting
red plum blossoms?

00:02:52.760 --> 00:02:55.020
Do you like plum blossoms, Your Majesty?

00:02:56.760 --> 00:02:57.640
Yes.

00:02:58.440 --> 00:03:00.170
My mother loved plum blossoms—

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:01.600
blooming in the cold,
proud and unyielding,

00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:02.800
crimson like blood.

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:05.820
How captivating they are.

00:03:07.440 --> 00:03:08.440
More captivating

00:03:08.560 --> 00:03:10.120
than me?

00:03:40.400 --> 00:03:41.240
Serve me

00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:43.000
well,

00:03:47.240 --> 00:03:48.640
just like they do.

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:51.900
Who knows—I might even
grant you the title of High Consort.

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:56.400
We

00:03:57.079 --> 00:03:58.810
have plenty of time ahead of us.

00:04:05.160 --> 00:04:07.640
The Queen truly favors Yun Zhan.

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:10.120
The affection in her eyes
is almost impossible to hide.

00:04:10.120 --> 00:04:11.600
With looks like Yun Zhan's,

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:12.680
forget the Queen—

00:04:12.680 --> 00:04:15.080
even you and I couldn't help
being tempted.

00:04:15.080 --> 00:04:15.800
Mr. Bai.

00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:17.000
Go.

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:47.800
Yun Zhan,

00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:50.050
you'd better behave yourself.

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:56.960
Such audacity.

00:04:57.880 --> 00:04:59.680
The Queen's status is supremely noble.

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:00.600
She is no pleasure-seeking noblewoman

00:05:00.600 --> 00:05:02.440
from the Slave House.

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:04.000
Know your place!

00:05:06.760 --> 00:05:08.080
We've always been intense,

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:09.040
Mr. Bai.

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:10.960
Who do you think you are?

00:05:10.960 --> 00:05:11.760
You...

00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:30.680
I may be nothing special—

00:05:30.680 --> 00:05:33.640
just a bit spoiled by the Queen's favor.

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:38.200
I am the Prime Minister's only son,

00:05:38.200 --> 00:05:39.400
born of a noble house.

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:41.860
Defying me is an act of insubordination.

00:05:42.159 --> 00:05:43.200
If I wished,

00:05:43.680 --> 00:05:45.680
I could take your life at any moment.

00:05:46.840 --> 00:05:47.880
Then the Queen

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:50.320
would be heartbroken.

00:06:19.420 --> 00:06:21.790
[Lu Ran, Medical Envoy of Mocheng]

00:06:25.760 --> 00:06:27.280
I'm Lu Ran, death guard of Dongli,

00:06:27.280 --> 00:06:28.560
pay my respects to Your Highness.

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:29.360
Rise quickly.

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:34.760
You have fallen into exile,
hiding in the martial world

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:37.720
as "Stone Yama the Rogue,"

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:39.770
and have suffered greatly,

00:06:39.960 --> 00:06:40.920
yet still had to

00:06:40.920 --> 00:06:43.050
endure humiliation at Bai Yu's hands.

00:06:43.280 --> 00:06:44.760
If he had not wounded me,

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:47.159
how could I have ever met you?

00:06:48.440 --> 00:06:49.600
General Lu,

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:51.280
since the fall of Dongli,

00:06:51.440 --> 00:06:54.080
you have remained
in the deep palace of Mocheng.

00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:55.810
It is you who have been wronged.

00:06:55.960 --> 00:06:57.120
For Dongli,

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:58.760
I will serve until death.

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:01.780
Your Highness,

00:07:02.520 --> 00:07:04.560
now that you've
successfully entered the palace,

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:05.880
what is our next move?

00:07:07.320 --> 00:07:08.120
Wait.

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:11.040
Wait?

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:14.120
Your Highness,

00:07:14.120 --> 00:07:14.840
why change the plan?

00:07:14.840 --> 00:07:15.970
Why not kill her now?

00:07:21.320 --> 00:07:22.480
I've learned

00:07:23.600 --> 00:07:24.880
that Feng Li possesses the formula

00:07:24.880 --> 00:07:25.960
for Feng Condensation Incense,

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:27.690
which can control men's minds.

00:07:28.360 --> 00:07:29.020
In Mocheng,

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:30.240
where women rule,

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:33.330
this evil incense has long
harmed the people.

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:35.540
We must wait for the right moment.

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:38.680
I will reclaim Dongli

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:40.880
and make Mocheng pay in blood.

00:07:41.720 --> 00:07:44.360
I will also obtain the formula
for the evil incense

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:45.600
and wipe out
both the Demon Lord and that incense

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:47.640
once and for all.

00:07:58.890 --> 00:08:01.560
[All Is for Benevolence]

00:08:01.560 --> 00:08:03.240
Lord Meng Wu of Mocheng

00:08:03.320 --> 00:08:03.960
instructed me

00:08:03.960 --> 00:08:05.340
to add a small dose of poison

00:08:05.340 --> 00:08:07.280
to the Queen's medicinal
decoction every day.

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:09.480
They scheme and vie against each other,

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:10.250
unaware that

00:08:10.640 --> 00:08:11.560
you are the ultimate beneficiary

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:13.120
waiting in the wings.

00:08:15.920 --> 00:08:17.520
The Demon Lord is meticulous

00:08:17.880 --> 00:08:19.340
and difficult to win over.

00:08:19.840 --> 00:08:21.370
Perhaps this is worth a try.

00:08:51.560 --> 00:08:52.520
You're here?

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:59.280
Your Majesty, how did you know it was me?

00:09:00.400 --> 00:09:02.480
Everyone carries a distinct scent—

00:09:02.920 --> 00:09:04.040
especially you.

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:27.480
Don't be nervous.

00:09:29.080 --> 00:09:30.140
Just acupressure,

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:32.980
to dispel dampness and cool your system.

00:09:45.800 --> 00:09:46.860
What are you doing?

00:09:50.680 --> 00:09:51.480
Your Majesty,

00:09:51.520 --> 00:09:52.960
your inner heat runs high.

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:54.600
While the tonic is strengthening,

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:55.330
too much of it

00:09:55.520 --> 00:09:57.250
can aggravate your inner heat.

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:00.580
My temper has been raging lately.

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:03.930
Perhaps killing a few
would serve to quell my temper.

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:07.850
That medicine is poisoned.

00:10:09.520 --> 00:10:10.400
Really?

00:10:11.400 --> 00:10:12.400
How could that be?

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:14.640
Who wants to harm me?

00:10:17.280 --> 00:10:19.140
If you wish to soothe your temper,

00:10:19.240 --> 00:10:20.000
perhaps

00:10:21.400 --> 00:10:22.660
you'll allow me to try.

00:10:23.960 --> 00:10:24.480
Try.

00:10:47.560 --> 00:10:48.620
Your Majesty, then

00:10:49.400 --> 00:10:50.730
you have to endure a bit.

00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:52.840
You want me to...

00:10:58.400 --> 00:10:58.920
What?

00:10:59.640 --> 00:11:01.440
Don't you like it, Your Majesty?

00:11:03.960 --> 00:11:05.160
I just think

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:06.730
it lacks intensity.

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:27.520
Father!

00:11:28.240 --> 00:11:29.040
Father!

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:32.800
Father!

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:35.160
Run!

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:36.000
Father!

00:11:36.920 --> 00:11:37.720
Father!

00:11:41.280 --> 00:11:42.760
Father!

00:11:48.240 --> 00:11:49.680
-Your Highness, go!
-Go!

00:11:50.360 --> 00:11:51.820
Don't be afraid, I'm here.

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:53.720
Sit here.

00:11:55.240 --> 00:11:56.160
Prime Minister Yun,

00:11:56.160 --> 00:11:57.200
weren't Dongli and Mocheng

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:58.840
here to sign an alliance?

00:11:59.280 --> 00:12:00.760
Why are they trying to kill us?

00:12:00.760 --> 00:12:01.680
Your Highness,

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:03.930
we've fallen into Mocheng's trap.

00:12:04.760 --> 00:12:06.560
They never meant to form an alliance.

00:12:06.560 --> 00:12:08.560
This was a ruse to lure us out
and silence us,

00:12:08.560 --> 00:12:09.880
to kill both you and His Majesty.

00:12:09.880 --> 00:12:11.480
I'll fight them to the death.

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:13.200
Your Highness, you must not!

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:16.370
Change clothes.

00:12:18.520 --> 00:12:19.380
Your Highness,

00:12:19.480 --> 00:12:20.600
from now on,

00:12:20.920 --> 00:12:22.440
you are my son Yun Zhan.

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:28.320
No.

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:29.440
How could I

00:12:29.440 --> 00:12:30.440
trade someone else's life

00:12:30.440 --> 00:12:31.440
for my own?

00:12:31.960 --> 00:12:32.560
Cang Lin,

00:12:32.840 --> 00:12:34.500
I was never meant to live long.

00:12:34.520 --> 00:12:35.580
Only if you survive

00:12:35.760 --> 00:12:38.000
will Dongli have a future.

00:12:38.760 --> 00:12:39.620
Remember this—

00:12:39.680 --> 00:12:40.880
no matter what happens,

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:41.840
you must live on

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:43.370
and restore Dongli.

00:12:43.680 --> 00:12:44.520
Crown Prince Cang Lin,

00:12:44.520 --> 00:12:46.180
I require you to swear an oath.

00:12:47.920 --> 00:12:51.320
I swear in the name
of the Dongli royal house:

00:12:51.680 --> 00:12:53.520
this debt of blood

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:55.880
will one day be repaid

00:12:56.800 --> 00:12:59.000
by Mocheng in kind.

00:13:03.840 --> 00:13:04.400
No.

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:07.640
I haven't obtained world-ruining
incense formula yet.

00:13:07.640 --> 00:13:08.760
She cannot die.

00:13:21.760 --> 00:13:22.840
Why did you stop?

00:13:25.720 --> 00:13:27.920
Those pressure points are enough.

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:29.480
Going any further

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:30.840
might harm you.

00:13:39.080 --> 00:13:40.240
It does feel much better now.